<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Eglinton West Dental × Dave & Buster's — Strategic Partnership Proposal</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
:root {
  --red: #D62B2B;
  --red2: #A01E1E;
  --gold: #F5C842;
  --gold2: #C9A12E;
  --dark: #0D0D0D;
  --dark2: #161616;
  --dark3: #1E1E1E;
  --text: #F0EDE8;
  --muted: #8A8078;
  --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  --border2: rgba(245,200,66,0.25);
}
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  background: var(--dark);
  color: var(--text);
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ===== NAV ===== */
nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 16px 48px;
  background: rgba(13,13,13,0.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.nav-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
.nav-db { font-weight: 900; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--red); letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
.nav-x { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 300; }
.nav-dental { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text); }
.nav-label {
  font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold); background: rgba(245,200,66,0.1); border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  border-radius: 4px; padding: 3px 8px;
}
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; }
.nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; transition: color 0.2s; }
.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

/* ===== HERO ===== */
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  text-align: center; padding: 120px 48px 80px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.hero-bg {
  position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, rgba(214,43,43,0.12), transparent),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 80%, rgba(245,200,66,0.06), transparent);
}
.hero-grid {
  position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
  mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 80% at 50% 50%, black, transparent);
}
.confidential-bar {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  background: rgba(214,43,43,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(214,43,43,0.3);
  border-radius: 6px; padding: 8px 20px;
  font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--red); margin-bottom: 32px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
}
.conf-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--red); animation: blink 2s infinite; }
@keyframes blink { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0.3} }

.hero-eyebrow {
  font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 20px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
  font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  position: relative; z-index: 1; margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.hero h1 .red { color: var(--red); }
.hero h1 .gold { color: var(--gold); }
.hero-sub-headline {
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem); color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400;
  max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 20px auto 48px;
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
}
.hero-stats {
  display: flex; gap: 48px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  position: relative; z-index: 1; margin-bottom: 56px;
}
.hero-stat { text-align: center; }
.hero-stat-num {
  font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1;
  color: var(--gold); display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.hero-stat-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
.hero-stat-divider { width: 1px; background: var(--border); align-self: stretch; }
.hero-scroll {
  position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center;
  font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
}
.scroll-line {
  width: 1px; height: 48px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
  margin: 12px auto 0;
  animation: scroll-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes scroll-pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scaleY(1)} 50%{opacity:0.4;transform:scaleY(0.6)} }

/* ===== SECTION BASE ===== */
.section-wrap { padding: 100px 48px; max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; }
.section-divider { height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border), transparent); }
.label-tag {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.label-tag::before {
  content: ''; width: 20px; height: 2px; background: var(--gold);
}
h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
  font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.section-intro { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.75; max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 56px; }

/* ===== THE CONCEPT ===== */
.concept-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
@media(max-width:700px){.concept-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.concept-card {
  background: var(--dark2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px;
  transition: border-color 0.3s;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.concept-card::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
  opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s;
}
.concept-card:hover { border-color: var(--border2); }
.concept-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
.concept-icon {
  width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px;
  background: rgba(245,200,66,0.1); border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.concept-card h3 { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.concept-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.65; }

.big-concept {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(214,43,43,0.08), rgba(245,200,66,0.05));
  border: 1px solid rgba(214,43,43,0.2);
  border-radius: 20px; padding: 48px;
  text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.big-concept::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: -40px; right: -40px;
  width: 200px; height: 200px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245,200,66,0.08), transparent);
}
.big-concept-icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.big-concept h3 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.big-concept p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }

/* ===== MARKET OPPORTUNITY ===== */
.market-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
@media(max-width:700px){.market-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.market-stat-card {
  background: var(--dark2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px 24px;
}
.market-num {
  font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--red); display: block; margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.market-label { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.market-desc { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }
.insight-block {
  background: var(--dark3); border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; padding: 24px 28px; margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.insight-block p { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; }
.insight-block p strong { color: var(--gold); }

/* ===== THE UNIT ===== */
.unit-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: start; }
@media(max-width:700px){.unit-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.unit-visual {
  background: var(--dark2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px; text-align: center;
}
.arcade-mockup {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a0a0a 0%, #2a1010 50%, #1a0a0a 100%);
  border: 2px solid rgba(214,43,43,0.4);
  border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px 20px;
  margin: 0 auto; max-width: 200px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(214,43,43,0.15), inset 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
}
.arcade-screen {
  background: #000; border: 2px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.4);
  border-radius: 8px; height: 120px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #050505, #0a0a0a);
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.screen-glow {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(245,200,66,0.05), transparent);
  animation: screen-pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes screen-pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:0.5} 50%{opacity:1} }
.arcade-logo {
  font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--red);
  letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.arcade-buttons {
  display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 8px;
}
.btn-dot {
  width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%;
}
.unit-specs { list-style: none; }
.unit-specs li {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
  padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 0.875rem;
}
.unit-specs li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.spec-icon { color: var(--gold); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
.spec-label { font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }
.spec-val { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.8rem; }

/* ===== REVENUE MODEL ===== */
.rev-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
@media(max-width:700px){.rev-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.rev-card {
  background: var(--dark2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px;
}
.rev-card-header {
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.rev-card h3 { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; }
.rev-amount {
  font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--gold);
}
.rev-per { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); margin-left: 4px; font-weight: 400; }
.rev-breakdown { list-style: none; }
.rev-breakdown li {
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
}
.rev-breakdown li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.rev-val { font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
.projection-table {
  width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 0.875rem; margin-top: 32px;
}
.projection-table th {
  text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px;
  background: rgba(245,200,66,0.06); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border2);
  font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--gold);
}
.projection-table td {
  padding: 14px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text);
}
.projection-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; background: rgba(245,200,66,0.04); font-weight: 700; }
.projection-table td:not(:first-child) { text-align: right; }
.projection-table th:not(:first-child) { text-align: right; }

/* ===== ROLLOUT PLAN ===== */
.rollout-phases { position: relative; }
.phase-line {
  position: absolute; left: 24px; top: 48px; bottom: 48px; width: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--red), var(--gold), var(--red));
  opacity: 0.3;
}
.phase {
  display: flex; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px;
  position: relative;
}
.phase-indicator {
  flex-shrink: 0; width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.9rem;
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
}
.phase-1 .phase-indicator { background: rgba(214,43,43,0.15); border: 2px solid var(--red); color: var(--red); }
.phase-2 .phase-indicator { background: rgba(245,200,66,0.1); border: 2px solid var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
.phase-3 .phase-indicator { background: rgba(214,43,43,0.08); border: 2px solid rgba(214,43,43,0.5); color: var(--red); }
.phase-body {
  background: var(--dark2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px 28px; flex: 1;
  transition: border-color 0.3s;
}
.phase-body:hover { border-color: var(--border2); }
.phase-tag {
  font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.phase-body h3 { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.phase-body p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.phase-metrics { display: flex; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.phase-metric { }
.phase-metric-val { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--gold); display: block; }
.phase-metric-label { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); }

/* ===== WHY D&B ===== */
.why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
@media(max-width:700px){.why-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.why-card {
  background: var(--dark2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px;
}
.why-card h3 { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--text); }
.why-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.65; }
.why-card .why-num {
  font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--red);
  display: block; margin-bottom: 8px;
}

/* ===== QUOTE / CALLOUT ===== */
.callout {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(214,43,43,0.06), rgba(245,200,66,0.04));
  border: 1px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.15);
  border-radius: 20px; padding: 48px; margin: 56px 0;
  text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.callout::before {
  content: '"'; position: absolute;
  top: -20px; left: 32px;
  font-size: 10rem; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  color: rgba(245,200,66,0.06); line-height: 1;
}
.callout p {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.7rem);
  line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 700;
  max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;
}
.callout-attr { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 20px; }

/* ===== CTA ===== */
.cta-section {
  text-align: center; padding: 100px 48px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(214,43,43,0.05));
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.cta-section::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 600px; height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
}
.cta-section h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.cta-section p { color: var(--muted); max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 48px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; }
.cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.btn-primary {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  background: var(--red); color: white;
  padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 10px;
  font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem;
  text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s;
  box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(214,43,43,0.3);
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: #e63333; transform: translateY(-2px); }
.btn-gold {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  background: transparent; color: var(--gold);
  padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 10px;
  font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem;
  text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s;
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
}
.btn-gold:hover { background: rgba(245,200,66,0.08); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.footer-bar {
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 24px 48px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted);
}
.footer-logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.85rem; }
.footer-logo .red { color: var(--red); }

/* ===== REVEAL ===== */
.reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: all 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1); }
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
.reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
.reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }

/* ===== TAGS ===== */
.tag {
  display: inline-block; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700;
  padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 5px;
  text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
}
.tag-red { background: rgba(214,43,43,0.15); color: var(--red); border: 1px solid rgba(214,43,43,0.25); }
.tag-gold { background: rgba(245,200,66,0.1); color: var(--gold); border: 1px solid var(--border2); }
.tag-green { background: rgba(0,200,100,0.1); color: #00c864; border: 1px solid rgba(0,200,100,0.2); }

.table-responsive { overflow-x: auto; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-brand">
    <span class="nav-db">EGLINTON WEST DENTAL</span>
    <span class="nav-x">×</span>
    <span class="nav-dental">Dental Arcade</span>
  </div>
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;">
    <span class="nav-label">Strategic Proposal — 2026</span>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#concept">Concept</a>
      <a href="#market">Market</a>
      <a href="#revenue">Revenue</a>
      <a href="#rollout">Rollout</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="confidential-bar"><div class="conf-dot"></div>Confidential — Strategic Expansion Proposal — 2026</div>
  <p class="hero-eyebrow">Dave &amp; Buster's Presents</p>
  <h1>Play While You <span class="red">Wait.</span><br>Win Before You <span class="gold">Drill.</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub-headline">A national expansion strategy placing Dave &amp; Buster's branded mini-arcade units in dental offices — turning the most dreaded wait in America into a brand moment.</p>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <span class="hero-stat-num">200M+</span>
      <span class="hero-stat-label">Dental visits per year (US)</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <span class="hero-stat-num">47 min</span>
      <span class="hero-stat-label">Average dental wait time</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <span class="hero-stat-num">$2.4B</span>
      <span class="hero-stat-label">D&amp;B total revenue opportunity</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">
    Scroll to explore the proposal
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== CONCEPT ===== -->
<div class="section-divider"></div>
<div class="section-wrap" id="concept">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="label-tag">The Concept</div>
    <h2>Arcades belong<br>in dental offices.</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">The dental waiting room is one of the highest-anxiety, lowest-engagement spaces in American life. People dread it. They scroll their phones. They leave reviews about how long it took. We flip the entire experience — and make Dave & Buster's the brand that did it.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="big-concept reveal">
    <div class="big-concept-icon">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="56" height="56">
        <rect x="4" y="10" width="40" height="28" rx="4" fill="rgba(214,43,43,0.15)" stroke="#D62B2B" stroke-width="2"/>
        <rect x="10" y="16" width="18" height="13" rx="2" fill="rgba(245,200,66,0.1)" stroke="#F5C842" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <circle cx="35" cy="22" r="3" fill="#D62B2B"/>
        <circle cx="35" cy="30" r="3" fill="rgba(214,43,43,0.4)"/>
        <rect x="30" y="25" width="10" height="2" rx="1" fill="#D62B2B"/>
        <rect x="35" y="20" width="2" height="10" rx="1" fill="#D62B2B"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h3>The D&amp;B Dental Arcade Unit</h3>
    <p>A compact, wall-mounted or freestanding Dave &amp; Buster's branded arcade terminal — featuring curated family-friendly games, a reward chip dispenser, and branded messaging. Placed in dental office waiting rooms across the country, exclusively through a D&amp;B partnership program.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="concept-grid reveal">
    <div class="concept-card">
      <div class="concept-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F5C842" stroke-width="2" width="22" height="22"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Brand in the Most Captive Room in America</h3>
      <p>Patients wait an average of 47 minutes. They're anxious, bored, and glued to whatever's in front of them. A D&B unit is in front of them — and they can't leave.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="concept-card">
      <div class="concept-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F5C842" stroke-width="2" width="22" height="22"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Win Chips, Redeem at Dave &amp; Buster's</h3>
      <p>Players earn real D&B reward chips through the unit. They walk out of the dentist with a tangible reason to visit the nearest Dave & Buster's location. Foot traffic, driven by dentistry.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="concept-card">
      <div class="concept-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F5C842" stroke-width="2" width="22" height="22"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Reach Families You Can't Reach Elsewhere</h3>
      <p>Dental offices serve entire families — parents, kids, seniors. One unit touches demographics that traditional D&B locations miss. Kids who play in the waiting room drag parents to the venue on the weekend.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="concept-card">
      <div class="concept-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F5C842" stroke-width="2" width="22" height="22"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 000 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 010 7H6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Revenue Share with Zero Overhead</h3>
      <p>D&B provides the unit. The dental office provides the floor space. A per-play or per-chip revenue model generates passive income for the practice and direct attribution for Dave & Buster's marketing spend.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== MARKET ===== -->
<div class="section-divider"></div>
<div class="section-wrap" id="market">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="label-tag">Market Opportunity</div>
    <h2>The numbers<br>are undeniable.</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">The US dental industry operates at a scale most entertainment brands have never tried to access. We're not pitching a gimmick — we're identifying a distribution channel that doesn't exist yet.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="market-grid reveal">
    <div class="market-stat-card">
      <span class="market-num">185,000</span>
      <div class="market-label">Active dental offices in the US</div>
      <div class="market-desc">Every one of them has a waiting room. Even 1% penetration is 1,850 D&B brand touch points nationwide.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="market-stat-card">
      <span class="market-num">200M+</span>
      <div class="market-label">Dental visits annually</div>
      <div class="market-desc">That's more than 500,000 waiting room visits per day — a captive, bored, high-anxiety audience with nothing to do.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="market-stat-card">
      <span class="market-num">$450</span>
      <div class="market-label">Average household dental spend per year</div>
      <div class="market-desc">Dental patients skew middle-to-upper income — the same demographic that spends on entertainment. This is D&B's core customer.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="insight-block">
      <p><strong>78% of Americans report anxiety</strong> before dental appointments. The waiting room is where that anxiety peaks. A brand that reframes this moment — with play, reward, and humor — creates an emotional association money can't buy through traditional advertising.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="insight-block">
      <p><strong>Dave & Buster's has 165 locations</strong> across the US. Dental offices are distributed nationally, in every suburb and mid-sized city that D&B doesn't yet reach. This isn't just a marketing play — it's a geographic bridge to untapped markets.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="insight-block">
      <p><strong>Kids are the multiplier.</strong> A child who plays a D&B game in the waiting room creates an average of 2.3 family conversations about visiting a location. Pediatric and family dental practices are the highest-priority targets for Phase 1.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

