<!-- ===== ROLLOUT ===== -->
<div class="section-divider"></div>
<div class="section-wrap" id="rollout">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="label-tag">Rollout Plan</div>
    <h2>How we get there<br>from here.</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">Three phases. Measured. Scalable. Built to accelerate at each milestone without overcommitting upfront capital.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="rollout-phases reveal">
    <div class="phase-line"></div>

    <div class="phase phase-1">
      <div class="phase-indicator">1</div>
      <div class="phase-body">
        <div class="phase-tag">Months 1–6 — Pilot</div>
        <h3>Prove It in 50 Practices</h3>
        <p>Deploy D&B Dental Arcade Units in 50 family and pediatric dental offices across 3 cities — ideally near existing D&B locations (Dallas, Chicago, Atlanta). Measure engagement, chip redemption rates, and conversion to in-store visits. Gather patient satisfaction data from dental office partners.</p>
        <div class="phase-metrics">
          <div class="phase-metric"><span class="phase-metric-val">50</span><span class="phase-metric-label">Pilot locations</span></div>
          <div class="phase-metric"><span class="phase-metric-val">3</span><span class="phase-metric-label">Target cities</span></div>
          <div class="phase-metric"><span class="phase-metric-val">6 mo</span><span class="phase-metric-label">Duration</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="phase phase-2">
      <div class="phase-indicator">2</div>
      <div class="phase-body">
        <div class="phase-tag">Months 7–18 — Regional Scale</div>
        <h3>500 Offices. 10 Markets.</h3>
        <p>Using pilot data, launch in 10 major metros. Prioritize suburban family practices (highest waiting room dwell time). Build a dedicated dental partner portal for practice owners to apply, track revenue share, and access marketing assets. Begin co-branded social campaign with dental influencers.</p>
        <div class="phase-metrics">
          <div class="phase-metric"><span class="phase-metric-val">500</span><span class="phase-metric-label">Active units</span></div>
          <div class="phase-metric"><span class="phase-metric-val">10</span><span class="phase-metric-label">Metro markets</span></div>
          <div class="phase-metric"><span class="phase-metric-val">$3.2M</span><span class="phase-metric-label">Projected ARR</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="phase phase-3">
      <div class="phase-indicator">3</div>
      <div class="phase-body">
        <div class="phase-tag">Year 2–5 — National Dominance</div>
        <h3>18,500 Offices. Everywhere.</h3>
        <p>Full national deployment through DSO (Dental Service Organization) partnerships. The top 10 DSOs in the US control over 10,000 locations. A single DSO partnership agreement gets D&B into thousands of waiting rooms overnight. Introduce the "D&B Dental Pass" — a combined dental membership + D&B loyalty program.</p>
        <div class="phase-metrics">
          <div class="phase-metric"><span class="phase-metric-val">18,500</span><span class="phase-metric-label">Total units</span></div>
          <div class="phase-metric"><span class="phase-metric-val">Top 10</span><span class="phase-metric-label">DSO partnerships</span></div>
          <div class="phase-metric"><span class="phase-metric-val">$118M+</span><span class="phase-metric-label">Projected ARR</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== WHY D&B ===== -->
<div class="section-divider"></div>
<div class="section-wrap">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="label-tag">Why Dave &amp; Buster's</div>
    <h2>No other brand<br>can do this.</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">This strategy only works because of what Dave & Buster's already is. The brand equity, the game library, the chip reward system, and the nationwide footprint are all prerequisites. D&B has them. Nobody else does.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="why-grid reveal">
    <div class="why-card">
      <span class="why-num">165</span>
      <h3>Existing D&B Locations Drive Redemption</h3>
      <p>Chips earned in the dental office need a place to be redeemed. D&B has 165 locations and growing. Every dental office within 30 miles of a D&B is a direct funnel.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <span class="why-num">40yr</span>
      <h3>Brand Heritage in Games and Fun</h3>
      <p>D&B has been synonymous with arcade games since 1982. That brand association is the entire product. A competitor trying to replicate this would need decades to build the same recognition.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <span class="why-num">100M+</span>
      <h3>Power Card Database for Attribution</h3>
      <p>D&B's Power Card loyalty system can track exactly which patients converted from dental office chip earners to in-store visitors. Full attribution. No guesswork.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <span class="why-num">Zero</span>
      <h3>No Competitor is in This Space</h3>
      <p>There is no company currently placing branded entertainment units in dental offices at scale. This is a first-mover opportunity. The category doesn't exist yet — D&B creates it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

